 Course Registration Management System

A simple Java project demonstrating **JDBC connectivity with MySQL** for managing student course registrations.  
This project is designed for beginners to understand how to connect Java applications to databases using JDBC.

---

## ğŸš€ Features
- Connects Java program to MySQL database  
- Creates the `registrations` table automatically (if it doesnâ€™t exist)  
- Inserts a sample student and course record  
- Displays all existing registrations in the console  
- Uses **JDBC PreparedStatement** for safe SQL operations  

